OL,3,C'Beloved' Scottish Borders railway
OL,4,Ccampaigner dies at the age of 95
OL,6,FA community stalwart who was behind
OL,7,Fthe campaign for the restoration of
OL,8,Fthe Borders Railway has died at the
OL,9,Fage of 95, her family has announced.
OL,11,FFor almost half a century, Madge
OL,12,FElliot MBE campaigned tirelessly
OL,13,Fagainst the closure of the Edinburgh-
OL,14,FHawick-Carlisle Waverley line in 1969
OL,15,Fand was a founding member of the
OL,16,FCampaign for Borders Rail.
