OL,3,C'Beloved' Scottish Borders railway
OL,4,Ccampaigner dies at the age of 95
OL,6,FThe campaign to restore the service
OL,7,Fwas led by Madge's son, Sean, who has
OL,8,Fdescribed his mum as "inspirational".
OL,10,FHe said: "After a 10 year battle with
OL,11,FAlzheimer's, our inspirational mum,
OL,12,FMadge, succumbed to a combination of
OL,13,Fold age and this awful disease on
OL,14,FSaturday morning.
